{
    "text": "\ud83d\udccc Save this for when you visit Paris \ud83c\uddeb\ud83c\uddf7\u2728  \ud83d\udccdCaf\u00e9 - Restaurant Le Jardin du Petit Palais  Located in the heart of my favorite museum, Petit Palais, this cafe is a hidden gem that you can\u2019t miss! When you visit, I highly recommend sitting on the terrace and soaking up the beauty of the museum, fountain, and garden while having a delicious lunch. Petit Palais is free to enter, so you can visit this cafe for free as well! \ud83c\udf74  Have you heard of this cafe before? \ud83e\udd0d  Follow @helloangelia for more travel tips around the world \u2728  #parisfrance #visitparis #exploreparis #exploreeurope #visiteurope #parisvibes #europetrip Paris France, Paris restaurant, travel reels, europe travel, European summer",
